In mathematics, the '''Al-Salam–Ismail polynomials''' are a family of [[orthogonal polynomials]] introduced by {{harvs|txt|last=Al-Salam|author1-link=Waleed Al-Salam|last2=Ismail|author2-link=Mourad Ismail|year=1983}}.

